@host = {{host}}
@token = {{token}}
@compartmentId = {{compartmentId}}

### PATCH — renombrar

PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/{{compartmentId}}/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Finanzas (renombrado)"
}

###

### PATCH — solo descripción

PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/compartments/{{compartmentId}}/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "description": ""
}
